      "writtenOn": "2019-11-27T08:31:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I investigate the trend of gRPC service names in Google3 with ttylenda@, and found that more than 50% of existing gRPC services are named with `Service` suffix. So I decided to mandate that services should be named with `Service` suffix.",
